{"tid":1534061,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"每朝早地鐵都有警察嘅話","createTime":"2019-09-03T01:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T04:09:17.000Z","uid":272528,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6fafaeb9880168004f810c626638f92e8ba525f7","tid":1534061,"uid":272528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:41:18.000Z","msg":"大家可以突登行過佢地面前，<br />\n俾一個鼓勵嘅眼神班警察，<br />\n仲可以口up up 咁講加油，<br />\n但千祈唔好出聲，廢事俾人話你撐警而俾人打<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有，記得係鼓勵嘅眼神，<br />\n<strong>用鄙視嘅眼神會令警察承受極大嘅精神壓力</strong>，<br />\n所以要小心啲唔好用錯眼神！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然香港無辱警罪，但大家唔好唔好講粗口同做粗口手勢，因為可能會干犯遊蕩罪、公眾地方行為不檢等嘅萬能key!!"},{"pid":"be01186d6ee38ac0e1c2d97230293c37a7988888","tid":1534061,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:43:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n寧鳴而死 不默而生<br />\n寧化飛灰 不作浮塵</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"34e031a6e1270565878c468ed42f88b2fad81fbc","tid":1534061,"uid":272528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:45:41.000Z","msg":"十連推嘅一"},{"pid":"e1ee1a5a7861b2ffb69dfa5230f7bd8c4ece0743","tid":1534061,"uid":157857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:51:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"49b32c2e8b37a5cd00b2dca802d89c3dd1b57c9c","tid":1534061,"uid":272528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:52:06.000Z","msg":"十連推嘅二"},{"pid":"4b7f61255a7914664aab095ceec029d6e0b9e440","tid":1534061,"uid":272528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:11:41.000Z","msg":"十連推嘅三"},{"pid":"bcd21c0893ae1b81150fc0625461c1b8b5936147","tid":1534061,"uid":272528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:22:34.000Z","msg":"十連推嘅四"},{"pid":"c35ddaa70082262b6e62f96084ace81487b38388","tid":1534061,"uid":272528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim